                                          Top Churn Reasons

                        BUSINESS QUESTION
What are the top reasons customers are churning across different churn categories?

               QUERY
SELECT
	Churn_Category,
	Churn_Reason,
	COUNT(*)affected_customers
FROM  telecom_customer 
GROUP BY Churn_Category,Churn_Reason
ORDER BY affected_customers DESC

                                    KEY FINGINGS
Most of our customers leave without any reason while a others leave for competitors. This suggests hidden issues in customer experience, 
pricing, or service value that are not being captured.

                             RECOMMENDATION
Our various team implement a feedback system that will help us better understand why customers are leaving. This can include exit surveys, follow-up calls,
or short feedback forms at the point of churn.
At the same time, since some customers are leaving for competitors,attitude. The company should review its pricing and service quality.
Improving customer experience at various department  will also help reduce unexplained churn.
